label: AB2_tI6_139_a_e-001
title: MoSi$_{2}$ ($C11_{b}$) Structure
comments: When $c=3a$ and $z_{2}=1/3$ the atoms are on the sites of \href{current_web_home_dir/A_cI2_229_a-001}{a body-centered cubic ($A2$) lattice}. For MoSi$_{2}$ itself, (Harada, 1998) gives $c/a = 2.45$ and $z_{2}=0.3353$. Other compounds in this structure have very different values of $c/a$ and even $z_{2}$.
